## General

**Name:**

**Status:** `active` 
 
**Description:** 
 
: [EN]  Nets is one of northern Europe's leading companies for payment solutions, information services and digital security solutions, with one of the most extensive and innovative product portfolios in Europe. Our ambition is to become an even stronger partner to our customers by supporting their business nationally as well as internationally. We want to make the handling of both financial and information assets easier and more secure. Find out more about us at www.nets.eu.
